{"id":151993,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/德国之声-在欧盟检测出中国危险商品数量创纪录/","date":"2011-05-13T00:30:32Z","modified":"2011-05-13T00:30:32Z","title":"德国之声 | 在欧盟检测出中国危险商品数量创纪录","content":"<div>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">布鲁塞尔</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">据法新社报道，欧洲去年发现的中国产危险商品数量超过以往任何一年。欧盟委员会周四（５月１２日）在公布</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">“</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">快速信息交换系统（</span><span>Rapid Exchange of Information System &#8211; RAPEX</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">”</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年度报告时指出，去年，欧盟共禁止、从市场上撤下或召回了创纪录的２２４４批次危险商品，其中一半以上来自中国（５８％），１７％来自欧盟成员国自己，１５％来自其他第三国，其余１０％的来源不明。</span><span>RAPEX</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">亦称</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">“</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">欧盟非食品类消费品快速警报系统</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">”</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，旨在保护消费者权益。该警告系统从２００４年问世以来，发出警报的商品数量从当年的４６８批次上升至去年的２２４４批次。报告指出，数字增加的原因并非危险商品数量增加，而是快速信息交换系统效率提高，从而减少了进入欧盟市场的危险商品数量。</span></p>\n</div>\n<p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" /><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" width=\"1\" /><a href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C15070018%2C00.html%3Fmaca%3Dchi-rss-chi-all-1127-rdf&#038;title=%E5%9C%A8%E6%AC%A7%E7%9B%9F%E6%A3%80%E6%B5%8B%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%8D%B1%E9%99%A9%E5%95%86%E5%93%81%E6%95%B0%E9%87%8F%E5%88%9B%E7%BA%AA%E5%BD%95\" rel=\"nofollow\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}